^ [1]
^ [2]
^ "horizontal market". Investorwords.com. 
^ http://www.bls.gov/iag/tgs/iag_index_naics.htm
^ http://unstats.un.org/unsd/cr/registry/isic-4.asp







 
						Retrieved from "https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Vertical_market&oldid=790243988"					
